# Copy to .env and adjust if needed. Never commit the real .env.
#
# SATOSWARM_MOCK is the ONLY mock/real switch in this project (read once,
# in src/tools/execution.py; every other module imports that constant).
#
#   1            = MOCK mode. No ROCm tools are invoked; simulated
#                  MI300X-shaped data is returned so the pipeline can be
#                  developed/tested on any machine (e.g. a Windows laptop).
#   0, or unset  = REAL mode. hipify-clang / hipcc / amd-smi are actually
#                  invoked via subprocess. Requires a real ROCm-capable GPU
#                  with those binaries on PATH (i.e. the MI300X pod).
#
# For the real hardware run: leave this unset, or set it to 0.
SATOSWARM_MOCK=1
